{"tid":896822,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[字海]我黎sir見會然言xxx終於唔盲反cy,終於可以安祥離去","createTime":"2018-11-10T11:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T13:16:13.000Z","uid":8307,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb9cfa60892fcc0795fe0cf33a3902b2a5eeef5","tid":896822,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"我諗清楚了，決定離開連登去嘗試新既人生.. <br />\n向過去既自己、興趣、生活說再見了.. <br />\n雖然每一位手足對我黎講都好重要，係有經歷過(全部動物台).. <br />\n每一位都係我在連登用時間同金錢去追求佢地，帶佢地返屋企和我同居... <br />\n純情的我，當然沒有和他們進行過多身體接觸，別說體液交流，什至連過多的身體接觸也沒有，最多也是每一位手足帶回家後係咁二身體接觸玩5秒，沒有任何色情成份.. <br />\n所以，絕對是99%全新處男清純男!!!!!!!!!! <br />\n<br />\n最後，唔好以為我打篇文好好笑係到當我派膠，我係好認真! <br />\n我既人生由自己決定，我要做一個有責任成熟認真既男生.. <br />\n所以依堆手足，就益大家吧，我要好好思考往後既人生... <br />\n以上係我潛水一個月既心得，我諗以後我都唔會點係動物台出聲了，原諒我，這是最後一次!"},{"pid":"b85cb238e5fcdc2454f36409d56731d7fc6532e6","tid":896822,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHbP93g.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHbP93g.gif&h=652b4ae4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69962d95b473be94f1e3074becba3ec567200384","tid":896822,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T11:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HrQxopm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrQxopm.gif&h=ecba990f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c6e8ab6f44ccffc76a68a8dfe208ba7712818fd","tid":896822,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T11:25:36.000Z","msg":"好行唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ea64d32dc807167cbe216c1d62575bf9958bcb","tid":896822,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c6e8ab6f44ccffc76a68a8dfe208ba7712818fd","tid":896822,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T11:25:36.000Z","ms